Lesson 12: Managing Software with Ansible 

1. Set up a repository on control.example.com
2. This repository should offer at least one file, including the nmap file
3. Provide a file list using variables
4. Configure ansible1 and ansible2 to use the repository that is provided through the package repository
5. Install the nmap package from this repository

