Lesson 16: Managing Networking	 

Manage networking:
1. Write a playbook that verifies that two network interfaces are avaliable
2. If  second interface is avaliable, the playbook should set it up with the network configuration and assign the IP address 192.168.4.30/24 
   on the interface   

